# gitleaks fingerprint ignore-list.
#
# Add one gitleaks "Fingerprint" per line to permanently ignore a specific
# finding that is a confirmed false positive (test fixture, example value,
# or an already-rotated credential). Fingerprints are printed by gitleaks
# and look like:
#
#   <commit-sha>:<file-path>:<rule-id>:<line-number>
#
# Prefer this over disabling rules or broadening the .gitleaks.toml
# allowlist, because it scopes the exception to a single finding.
